<h2 id="overhaul-datagov">Overhaul Data.gov</h2>

<p><a href="https://data.gov">Data.gov</a>, managed by the U.S. General Services Administration, is the central repository for official government data. While GSA doesn’t have enforcement authority over agency open data publishing, it does play a major role in projecting the health of the federal government’s open data efforts.</p>

<p>Since its inception, Data.gov has changed very little, both on the technical and user experience fronts. It’s upkeep is</p>

